{"tid":1604844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 點解要等政府宣布係乜狀態","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:51.000Z","uid":268692,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db249ec88e4e5e58701d1440e78c1b7c9dcae6b4","tid":1604844,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"外國朋友傾計想問下連登仔 冇ac代出po<br />\n<br />\n基本上依家日日都有防暴 反政府既人係街乜都冇做<br />\n冇原因都被拉 大家諗下攬炒plan 就係迫佢宣布戒嚴<br />\n但依家唔宣布但照做 法律上佢地已經無視 老實講係冇乜野可以做 不過都要照出黎 <br />\n如其係咁 點解唔係咁很重要既日子係全世界鏡頭前面幫政府宣布戒嚴或者將來更嚴重既狀態<br />\n<br />\n同朋友講左p牌冇人理 佢話唔緊要睇唔睇到係緣份喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20c7d98bfe5611806221934ff4e7a085a703504","tid":1604844,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"我睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係推唔到"},{"pid":"77d7a91278f5e96d71cfa0a3bc7ecb1436b50346","tid":1604844,"uid":305010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:54:46.000Z","msg":"呢個諗法唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d8db9caa75bf67785be9d8e4de8d193f0c0ff9","tid":1604844,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d20c7d98bfe5611806221934ff4e7a085a703504","tid":1604844,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"我睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係推唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:55:25.000Z","msg":"緣份 睇到既人就睇到 睇下幾多有緣人可以跳出框框"},{"pid":"7530dcd8002a9b28763fba7bb7b1436494b28334","tid":1604844,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"得p牌見到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif